  "title": "fix minor spelling errors",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\nThis PR fixes a couple of comma errors in the `/documentation/` and `/about/` docs pages.\r\nThere are no linked issues to my knowledge.\r\n\r\n**Note**\r\nFor some reason, the GitHub highlighter does not show the exact changes on `line 8` in the `docs/about.md`. To speed-up the check, here is what was changed on line 8:\r\n\r\n```\r\nFor example [secured API Keys]\r\n->\r\nFor example, [secured API Keys]`\r\n```\r\n```\r\nthe UI itself is complex and time consuming because\r\n->\r\nthe UI itself is complex and time-consuming because\r\n```",
